{"tid":2003829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"辯方：雷射筆當武器不合邏輯","createTime":"2020-05-06T05:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:56:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3bc95e51e6e197b25d68c1c9023ba3357ac8ad4","tid":2003829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200506/I6ZFGHI3MF4XBFONKLHHEBEMWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FI6ZFGHI3MF4XBFONKLHHEBEMWY%2F&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=fbc4c863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FI6ZFGHI3MF4XBFONKLHHEBEMWY%2F&h=207ed548\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200506/I6ZFGHI3MF4XBFONKLHHEBEMWY/</a><br />\n<br />\n辯方：雷射筆當武器不合邏輯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588696611_208f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588696611_208f.jpg&h=b428d2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高等法院<br />\n<br />\n【少年藏械案上訴】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】9.21「光復屯門公園」遊行開始前，15歲少年被警員搜出藏有雷射筆及疑經改裝的雨傘與行山杖，早前被裁定有意圖管有攻擊性武器及公眾地方管有攻擊性武器兩................裝，而且過份推論少年藏有雷射筆必然是意圖作為攻擊性武器。法官潘敏琦聽取陳詞後，擇日頒下判決。<br />\n<br />\n代表上訴人的資深大狀彭耀鴻昨陳詞表示，上訴人案發時不足16歲，警..............下查問他，原審裁判官蘇惠德竟接納有關內容呈堂，更主動提出修改控罪，做法不公。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱官接納沒警誡口供不公<br />\n<br />\n彭耀鴻又指，雷射筆是用於「指出」某個位置，根本不適宜用作攻擊性武器，去年8月就有人用雷射筆照射太空館外面表達.....................射筆是攻擊性武器，並認定上訴人有意圖利用雷射筆作攻擊之用，完全不合邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n至於雨傘和行山杖，彭指兩者皆已破爛，上訴人帶在身上，可以只.................改裝作攻擊用途。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA13/20<br />\n■記者蔡少玲"},{"pid":"742cc015bd66d2dd10ed2ad7fcb9111f3573a66b","tid":2003829,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb31130b0